Package com.example.chicksevent.misc

Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.chicksevent.misc.User
com.example.chicksevent.misc.Entrant
public class Entrant extends User
Represents an entrant (participant) within the ChicksEvent system.

An Entrant corresponds to a user who can join or leave waiting lists for specific events, and whose participation status is tracked via EntrantStatus. The class also provides helper methods for updating Firebase Realtime Database entries within the "WaitingList" and "Event" roots.

Responsibilities:

  • Join or leave a waiting list for a given event.
  • Swap between waiting list states (e.g., WAITING â†’ INVITED).
  • Provide identification of the entrant within Firebase.

Firebase structure: Data is organized under: 

 WaitingList/{eventId}/{EntrantStatus}/{entrantId}
